cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this audit harness or cite the LoCoMo Audit findings, please cite it as below."
title: "There Is No Single LoCoMo Score: A Standardized, Vendor-Audited Re-evaluation of LLM Memory Systems"
abstract: >-
  An independent, reproducible evaluation harness for AI-memory systems, and a
  forensic audit of the public LoCoMo benchmark dispute. Decomposes four
  methodological forks responsible for 67%–92% vendor score divergence and
  specifies one frozen, fair, fully-reproducible protocol. Includes a $0
  keyless retrieval floor verifiable on real LoCoMo data today.
type: software
authors:
